# env files (NEVER commit credentials)
# NOTE: `.env.example` and `.env.local.example` are the ONLY env files
# permitted in the tree — they must contain placeholders, never real
# values. Every other .env variant is ignored to prevent secret leaks.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.local.example

